text: Panevėžys County is one of the ten counties in Lithuania. The capital city is Panevėžys. On 1 July 2010, the county administration was ended. == Municipalities == Panevėžys County has the following municipalities: Biržai district municipality Kupiškis district municipality Panevėžys city municipality Panevėžys district municipality Pasvalys district municipality Rokiškis district municipality ==References== Category:Counties of Lithuania
title: Panevėžys County
